Package cs1c

Class SongEntry

java.lang.Object
cs1c.SongEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<SongEntry>
public class SongEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<SongEntry>
One object of class SongEntry stores a simplified version of the genre data set from the Million Song Dataset. http://labrosa.ee.columbia.edu/millionsong/blog/11-2-28-deriving-genre-dataset
